WEBVTT

00:01.130 --> 00:02.859
PREVIOUSLY
ON "VERONICA MARS"...

00:02.870 --> 00:04.394
LATER, DEPUTY.

00:04.400 --> 00:06.732
ALICIA AND I
TALKED ABOUT IT.
WALLACE'S MOM?!

00:10.170 --> 00:12.229
I KNOW YOU BLAME ME
FOR YOUR MOTHER'S DEATH.

00:12.240 --> 00:14.128
SHE WAS YOUR MOM,
MY STEPMOM.

00:14.140 --> 00:15.437
DAD COULD HAVE USED YOU.

00:15.440 --> 00:17.146
NOW YOU'RE WORRIED
ABOUT DAD'S WELFARE?

00:17.150 --> 00:21.246
ISN'T HE THE BIG BAD WOLF --
CIGARETTE BURNS, BROKEN NOSES?

00:21.250 --> 00:23.445
I NEVER
WOULD HAVE HURT HER.
LILLY AND WEEVIL?

00:23.450 --> 00:25.418
LILLY IS DEAD!
HER KILLER IS IN JAIL!

00:25.420 --> 00:26.717
ABEL KOONTZ
DIDN'T KILL LILLY.

00:26.720 --> 00:28.153
YOU THINK
I KILLED LILLY.

00:28.160 --> 00:29.684
YOU HAVEN'T SEEN DUNCAN,
HAVE YOU?

00:29.690 --> 00:30.884
HE'S MISSING.

00:30.890 --> 00:33.654
BOB SELLS A HOUSE
FOR $136,000.

00:33.660 --> 00:37.266
IF HE MAKES 5% COMMISSION
FOR EVERY HOUSE HE SELLS,

00:37.270 --> 00:40.159
HOW MUCH MONEY DID BOB EARN
ON THIS SALE?

00:40.170 --> 00:44.004
ALL I KNOW IS
IF YOUR BOY BOB ONLY GETS 5%,

00:44.010 --> 00:46.638
HE'S PUSHING
THE WRONG PRODUCT.

00:47.640 --> 00:50.302
CAN I GET SOMETHING
TO WRITE WITH HERE?

00:50.310 --> 00:53.108
FIRST FUNDAMENTAL
OF FUNDAMENTALS OF MATH,

00:53.120 --> 00:56.647
ALWAYS CARRY
YOUR WRITING UTENSIL.

00:56.650 --> 01:00.359
SO, I HEARD
DUNCAN KANE TOOK OFF, HUH?

01:02.020 --> 01:03.681
I BELIEVE
THE OFFICIAL STORY

01:03.690 --> 01:06.853
INVOLVED A SICK RELATIVE
IN CHATI'ANOOGA.

01:06.860 --> 01:08.555
BUT, YEAH, HE TOOK OFF.

01:08.560 --> 01:10.118
HMM.

01:10.130 --> 01:12.234
WELL, THE WORD IS,
HE BOLTED

01:12.240 --> 01:15.630
'CAUSE YOU ACCUSED HIM
OF KILLING LILLY.

01:16.870 --> 01:18.929
WELL, WORD IS WRONG.

01:18.940 --> 01:20.339
HMM.

01:20.340 --> 01:23.047
BUT YOU DON'T THINK
THEY GOT THE RIGHT GUY?

01:23.050 --> 01:24.642
[ DOOR OPENS ]

01:26.120 --> 01:28.680
HEY, HONEY.

01:28.680 --> 01:30.739
ELI.

01:30.750 --> 01:32.456
SHERIFF.

01:33.490 --> 01:37.529
I'M JUST GIVING WEEVIL A
REFRESHER FOR HIS QUIZ TOMORROW.

01:39.030 --> 01:41.794
WELL,
I GUESS I'M REFRESHED.

01:41.800 --> 01:43.859
SEE YOU AT SCHOOL.

01:51.970 --> 01:53.506
HONEY...

01:53.510 --> 01:55.899
DO I NEED TO RECAP
MY CONCERNED-DAD LECTURES?

01:55.910 --> 01:59.346
NO RUNNING WITH SCISSORS,
NO CANDY FROM STRANGERS,

01:59.350 --> 02:01.443
NO SMARTENING UP
THE LOCAL CRIMINAL ELEMENT.

02:01.450 --> 02:05.079
HE HELPED ME OUT IN THE PAST.
I'M JUST RETURNING THE FAVOR.

02:05.090 --> 02:06.387
SAY YOU CALL IT EVEN.

02:06.390 --> 02:08.585
I'LL BE AT HOME...

02:08.590 --> 02:11.718
WITH THE ONLY SANE MEMBER
OF THE MARS FAMILY.

02:11.730 --> 02:15.848
THE ONE WHO EATS GARBAGE AND
KEEPS BRINGING ME DEAD BIRDS?

02:15.860 --> 02:16.997
THAT'S THE ONE.

02:17.000 --> 02:18.991
[ SIGHS ]

02:19.000 --> 02:21.764
[ BARKING ]

02:32.080 --> 02:34.241
[ DOG WHIMPERS ]

02:39.960 --> 02:41.416
CHESTER?!

02:41.420 --> 02:43.752
CHESTER, COME HERE, BOY!

02:43.760 --> 02:45.887
COME HERE, BABY!

02:45.890 --> 02:47.027
CHESTER!

02:47.030 --> 02:48.122
CHESTER!

02:48.130 --> 02:50.223
CH ESTE-E-E-R!

02:51.030 --> 02:53.134
OH. HEY.

02:53.140 --> 02:54.596
HEY.

02:55.440 --> 02:57.431
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

02:57.440 --> 02:59.169
LIKE, IN GENERAL?

02:59.170 --> 03:02.879
OR IS THERE A SPECIFIC ARENA
IN WHICH YOU'D LIKE MY OPINION?

03:02.880 --> 03:05.405
DO YOU THINK DUNCAN
IS JUST COOLING OFF,

03:05.410 --> 03:07.446
OR IS HE HOLED UP
IN SOME HOTEL ROOM

03:07.450 --> 03:08.849
POURING PEROXIDE
ON HIS HAIR

03:08.850 --> 03:11.341
AND TRYING TO FILE
HIS FINGERPRINTS OFF?

03:11.350 --> 03:13.784
HONESTLY,
I HAVE NO IDEA.

03:13.790 --> 03:15.678
I GOT THE CALL
FROM CELESTE TODAY,

03:15.690 --> 03:18.454
WANTING TO KNOW WHERE I THOUGHT
HE MIGHT HAVE GONE.

03:18.460 --> 03:19.893
WHAT'D YOU TELL HER?

03:19.900 --> 03:22.050
THE TRUTH --

03:22.060 --> 03:24.494
I DON'T KNOW.

03:28.070 --> 03:30.163
[ SCHOOL BELL RINGS ]

03:30.170 --> 03:31.660
SEE YA.

03:35.610 --> 03:37.305
Veronica:
ALL RIGHTY, LOGAN,

03:37.310 --> 03:39.870
WE'LL JUST SKIP OVER THE
TWO MINUTES IN HEAVEN WE HAD.

03:39.880 --> 03:42.314
YOU WANT TO PRETEND
IT NEVER HAPPENED?

03:42.320 --> 03:44.015
NO ARGUMENT HERE.

03:44.020 --> 03:48.684
MY LIPS, FOR ALL INTENTS
AND PURPOSES, ARE SEALED.

03:54.400 --> 03:56.960
SORRY,
THIS WAS ON YOUR...

03:56.970 --> 03:58.096
OH, THANKS.

03:58.100 --> 04:00.898
YOU'RE VERONICA MARS,
RIGHT?

04:00.900 --> 04:02.401
SOMETIMES.

04:02.410 --> 04:05.709
DO YOU THINK I COULD HIRE YOU
TO HELP ME FIND MY DOG?

04:05.710 --> 04:08.474
THAT DEPENDS.
WAS HE CHEATING ON YOU?

04:09.310 --> 04:11.778
LOST DOGS AREN'T REALLY
MY SPECIALTY.

04:11.780 --> 04:12.769
OH.

04:12.780 --> 04:16.011
OKAY, WELL,
THANKS ANYWAYS.

04:20.820 --> 04:24.153
YOU KNOW, MAYBE I COULD MAKE
A COUPLE PHONE CALLS

04:24.160 --> 04:25.957
OR MAYBE HELP
WITH SIGNAGE.

04:25.960 --> 04:27.427
EXCUSE ME A SEC.

04:27.430 --> 04:28.624
BREAKING NEWS.

04:28.630 --> 04:30.495
RECORD THIS DATE
IN HISTORY.

04:30.500 --> 04:32.730
FIRST TIME WALLACE FENNEL
GOT THE 4-1-1

04:32.740 --> 04:34.935
BEFORE THE LITTLE BIRDIE
GOT IT TO YOU.

04:34.940 --> 04:37.704
DO I HAVE TO TIP YOU OVER,
OR ARE YOU GONNA SPILL IT?

04:37.710 --> 04:39.678
CLEMMONS JUST GOT
A CALL.

04:39.680 --> 04:42.604
WEEVIL BROKE INTO THE KANE HOUSE
LAST NIGHT.

04:42.610 --> 04:46.740
NEIGHBORHOOD PATROL CAUGHT HIM
IN LILLY KANE'S BEDROOM.

04:48.950 --> 04:52.989
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

04:52.990 --> 04:59.281
* BUT I HAVEN'T THOUGHT OF YOU
LATELY AT ALL *

04:59.290 --> 05:01.599
* COME ON, NOW, SUGAR *

05:01.600 --> 05:04.364
* BRING IT ON, BRING IT ON,
YEAH *

05:04.370 --> 05:07.191
* JUST REMEMBER ME WHEN *

05:07.200 --> 05:09.088
* WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

05:09.100 --> 05:14.879
* A LONG TIME AGO,
WE USED TO BE FRIENDS *

05:22.250 --> 05:25.310
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

05:28.120 --> 05:30.122
HI. HOW ARE YOU.

05:30.130 --> 05:31.927
BETI'ER. . . NOW.

05:31.930 --> 05:33.898
I HAVEN'T HEARD FROM YOU
IN A COUPLE DAYS.

05:33.900 --> 05:37.290
ABOUT TO SHOW UP AT YOUR PLACE
WITH MY TOOLS OF RESTRAINT.

05:37.300 --> 05:38.824
WOULDN'T RECOMMEND IT.

05:38.830 --> 05:41.333
DAD USUALLY LIKES TO HAVE A GUY
TO DINNER AT LEAST ONCE

05:41.340 --> 05:42.739
BEFORE HE CUFFS ME.

05:42.740 --> 05:45.106
SO, WHAT CAN I HELP YOU WITH,
MISS MARS?

05:45.110 --> 05:48.329
MY SCHEDULE? SURE.
I'M OFF THURSDAY AND FRIDAY.

05:48.340 --> 05:50.604
UM, I'M ACTUALLY HERE
TO SEE WEEVIL.

05:50.610 --> 05:53.511
DO YOU THINK I COULD
GET A MINUTE WITH HIM?

05:56.250 --> 05:58.013
WHAT IS IT
ABOUT BAD BOYS?

05:58.020 --> 06:02.059
UM, TATTOOS, LEATHER,
PAROLE VIOLATIONS --

06:02.060 --> 06:03.425
TOTAL GOOD-GIRL BAIT.

06:03.430 --> 06:05.057
I'M DOOMED.

06:05.060 --> 06:08.723
HEY, YOU WERE HERE WHEN WEEVIL
WAS BROUGHT IN, RIGHT?

06:08.730 --> 06:10.266
WHAT DID THEY FIND ON HIM?

06:10.270 --> 06:14.991
THE BADASS STANDARDS --
17 CENTS, COUPLE CONDOMS, A PEN.

06:21.610 --> 06:25.546
DO YOU HAVE THAT NAIL FILE
AND J.LO POSTER I ASKED FOR?

06:27.280 --> 06:28.838
WHY WERE YOU
IN LILLY'S ROOM?

06:28.850 --> 06:31.080
WHAT BETTER HOUSE
FOR SOME B&E?

06:31.090 --> 06:34.218
I KNOW ABOUT YOU AND LILLY.
I KNOW ABOUT THE LETTERS.

06:34.220 --> 06:35.812
YEAH?

06:35.820 --> 06:37.879
WHATEVER YOU KNOW,
THAT'S NOT ALL THERE IS TO IT.

06:37.890 --> 06:40.120
I TELL YOU THAT I'M CLOSE
TO FINDING LILLY'S KILLER,

06:40.130 --> 06:42.667
AND TWO HOURS LATER,
YOU'RE BREAKING INTO HER ROOM.

06:42.670 --> 06:43.967
WHAT DO YOU EXPECT ME
TO THINK?

06:43.970 --> 06:45.790
I TOLD YOU
WHAT I WAS DOING THERE.

06:45.800 --> 06:48.837
NOW, IF YOU DON'T WANT TO
BELIEVE ME, THAT'S ON YOU, OKAY?

06:48.840 --> 06:50.603
YOU GONNA HELP ME OR NOT?

06:53.240 --> 06:54.502
NO.

06:55.910 --> 06:58.140
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT!
HOLD ON!

07:01.850 --> 07:02.919
DIAMOND RING.

07:02.920 --> 07:04.547
YOU BROKE IN
TO STEAL A RING?

07:04.550 --> 07:07.781
I WAS TRYING TO GET IT BACK.
IT'S MY MOTHER'S.

07:07.790 --> 07:10.679
SHE WAS SAVING IT FOR ME
AS AN ENGAGEMENT RING.

07:10.690 --> 07:12.692
AT ONE TIME,
I WAS DUMB ENOUGH

07:12.700 --> 07:15.351
TO THINK I WANTED LILLY
TO HAVE IT.

07:15.360 --> 07:17.123
FIND IT?

07:17.130 --> 07:19.325
NOPE.

07:19.330 --> 07:23.505
LOOK, UH, THE KANES WANT ME
CRUCIFIED FOR THIS.

07:23.510 --> 07:25.432
AND NOW THAT I'M 18...

07:25.440 --> 07:27.101
GOODBYE, JUVIE.

07:27.110 --> 07:29.431
HELLO, COMMUNITY SOAP.

07:29.440 --> 07:32.546
YEAH.

07:33.720 --> 07:36.518
NOW I SEE
HOW CRAPPY MINE WAS.

07:36.520 --> 07:38.112
IT WAS HEARTFELT CRAPPY.

07:38.120 --> 07:41.180
SO, TELL ME MORE ABOUT THE NIGHT
CHESTER DISAPPEARED.

07:41.190 --> 07:42.555
YOUR FRONT GATE WAS OPEN?

07:42.560 --> 07:43.857
NOT MINE -- THE MCDEEDS'.

07:43.860 --> 07:45.953
I BABYSIT THEIR SON, RYDER,
TWICE A WEEK.

07:45.960 --> 07:48.053
THEY LET ME KEEP CHESTER
IN THEIR YARD.

07:48.060 --> 07:49.925
HOW FAR DO YOU LIVE
FROM THEM?

07:49.930 --> 07:51.966
FAR.
I'M MORE LIKE AN 02er.

07:51.970 --> 07:55.929
SO, YOU PUT UP FLIERS.
DID YOU CHECK THE POUND?

07:55.940 --> 07:57.601
I CALLED
AND LEFI' MY NUMBER.

07:57.610 --> 07:59.771
YOU SHOULD GO DOWN THERE,
GIVE THEM A FLIER.

07:59.780 --> 08:01.304
IF THEY MEET YOU,
THEY'RE MORE LIKELY

08:01.310 --> 08:04.199
TO REMEMBER YOU AND CHESTER
IF HE COMES THROUGH.

08:11.750 --> 08:13.354
HEY, SWEETH EART.

08:13.360 --> 08:16.750
STAY CLOSE, OKAY? BARRY'S
GONNA BE HERE ANY MINUTE.

08:16.760 --> 08:18.728
RESEARCH
FOR YOUR NEXT ROLE?

08:18.730 --> 08:19.924
[ CHUCKLES SOFI'LY ]

08:19.930 --> 08:22.148
NO, PHIL JACKSON
GAVE ME THIS.

08:22.160 --> 08:25.527
HE SAID IT WOULD
CHANGE MY PERSPECTIVE.

08:25.530 --> 08:27.464
MAYBE YOU COULD OPTION IT.

08:27.470 --> 08:29.097
[ SCOFFS ]

08:29.100 --> 08:32.934
NOBODY SEEMS TO BELIEVE ME,
NOT EVEN MY OWN CHILDREN!

08:32.940 --> 08:35.170
I'M DONE ACTING, TRINA.

08:35.180 --> 08:37.501
THAT'S BEHIND ME NOW.

08:37.510 --> 08:41.276
BUT WHAT IF SOMETHING
SO GREAT CAME ALONG?

08:41.280 --> 08:45.011
THERE IS NOTHING GREATER
THAN LIVING IN THE MOMENT,

08:45.020 --> 08:47.682
BEING HERE
FOR THE ONES I LOVE.

08:47.690 --> 08:50.727
THAT'S MY JOB NOW.

08:53.760 --> 08:57.196
PUSH IN ON OUR HERO.

08:58.030 --> 09:00.897
NATURAL LIGHT FRAMES
HIS HANDSOME WEATHERED FACE

09:00.900 --> 09:04.734
AS HE PASSES SAGE ADVICE
TO HIS DOTING DAUGHTER.

09:04.740 --> 09:07.777
THE MUSIC SWELLS.

09:07.780 --> 09:11.602
[ Imitating Yoda ] IMPORTANT
YOUR FAMILY IS. HMM, HMM!

09:13.580 --> 09:16.048
BUT, DADDY,
THERE'S THIS TERRIFIC PART.

09:16.050 --> 09:17.688
IT'S THE VILLAIN
IN THIS FEATURE

09:20.120 --> 09:21.212
"ESCAPING YOUR PAST."

09:21.220 --> 09:23.051
YOU'D BE PERFECT.
TWO DAYS' WORK.

09:23.060 --> 09:25.051
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
HOLD ON, TRINA.

09:25.060 --> 09:28.291
THANK YOU FOR THINKING OF ME,
REALLY.

09:28.300 --> 09:32.122
BUT THIS -- THIS IS
WHAT I WANT TO BE DOING NOW.

09:32.130 --> 09:33.062
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

09:33.070 --> 09:34.890
I'M NOT SURE
IF YOU'RE AWARE,

09:34.900 --> 09:39.303
BUT LYNN UPDATED HER WILL
A FEW WEEKS BEFORE HER...DEATH.

09:39.310 --> 09:41.073
AARON, YOU WERE REMOVED.

09:41.080 --> 09:44.140
HMM.
WELL, I DIDN'T KNOW THAT,

09:44.150 --> 09:47.642
BUT, UH...WELL,
IT DOESN'T SURPRISE ME.

09:47.650 --> 09:49.174
IT'S COOL, BAR.

09:49.180 --> 09:52.513
DAD'S ACCOUNTANTS DIDN'T GIVE
MOM MUCH OF AN ALLOWANCE.

09:52.520 --> 09:55.512
ALL RIGHT, I'LL SKIP TO
THE RELEVANT PARAGRAPH HERE.

09:55.520 --> 09:59.627
"TO MY SON, LOGAN,
I BEQUEATH MY ART COLLECTION

09:59.630 --> 10:02.622
"AS WELL AS ALL OF MY
PERSONAL EFFECTS IN THE HOUSE.

10:02.630 --> 10:07.238
"IN ADDITION, I LEAVE HIM THE
BALANCE IN MY INVESTMENT ACCOUNT

10:07.240 --> 10:10.937
HELD WITH J.P. MORGAN,
TOTALING $115,000."

10:14.180 --> 10:17.172
AND ME?
SHE TOOK ME OUT, TOO?

10:18.110 --> 10:21.341
I'M AFRAID
YOU WERE NEVER IN IT.

10:23.420 --> 10:26.583
WE'RE LOOKING FOR A LOST
JACK RUSSELL TERRIER -- CHESTER.

10:26.590 --> 10:28.558
ANY CHANCE
HE'S COME THROUGH?

10:28.560 --> 10:29.925
PUREBRED JACK...

10:29.930 --> 10:32.751
HASN'T COME THROUGH.
SORRY.

10:32.760 --> 10:34.227
VERONICA MARS?

10:34.230 --> 10:36.892
J-DUB, THIS IS THE COOLEST GIRL
IN NEPTUNE HIGH.

10:36.900 --> 10:38.390
SHE WAS GONNA GET EXPELLED

10:38.400 --> 10:40.539
FOR PLANTING A SPY CAM
IN THE TEACHERS LOUNGE,

10:40.540 --> 10:43.304
BUT SHE HAD SO MUCH DIRT,
THEY JUST LET HER OFF.

10:43.310 --> 10:44.368
IS THAT SO?

10:44.370 --> 10:46.099
HAVE YOU SEEN MY DOG?

10:46.110 --> 10:48.271
UM...

10:49.680 --> 10:51.204
UH, MAN, NO.

10:51.210 --> 10:53.770
AW, I WISH I HAD, THOUGH.
WHAT A CUTIE.

10:53.780 --> 10:54.974
I'LL KEEP AN EYE OUT.

10:54.980 --> 10:56.618
WE'D REALLY
APPRECIATE THAT.

10:56.620 --> 10:58.144
THAN KS.
HANS.

10:58.150 --> 10:59.879
HANS.

10:59.890 --> 11:02.279
YOU REALLY HID A CAMERA
IN THE TEACHERS LOUNGE?

11:02.290 --> 11:04.622
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT HE'S TALKING ABOUT.

11:04.630 --> 11:05.949
OH.

11:06.830 --> 11:09.924
GOOD MORNING, BRO.
POP TART?

11:09.930 --> 11:12.319
HMM,
A TART FROM A TART.

11:12.330 --> 11:15.731
HE OF THE SICKLE WIT.
CAN I ASK YOU SOMETHING?

11:15.740 --> 11:18.163
HMM.
WOULD YOU LOOK AT THAT?

11:18.170 --> 11:22.038
THERE WAS A STRING ATTACHED
TO MY POP TART.

11:22.040 --> 11:24.838
YEAH. WELL,
I'M IN A LITTLE BIT OF A JAM.

11:24.850 --> 11:26.602
I COULD USE A LOAN.

11:26.610 --> 11:28.510
[ WATCH BEEPS ]

11:28.520 --> 11:32.183
12 HOURS TO HIT ME UP
FOR MY DEAD MOTHER'S MONEY.

11:33.820 --> 11:35.356
I WONDER WHO HAD THAT
IN THE POOL.

11:35.360 --> 11:39.251
YOU KNOW I WOULDN'T ASK
IF IT WASN'T IMPORTANT.

11:39.260 --> 11:40.591
OH, I DO. I DO.

11:40.600 --> 11:44.559
COULD I JUST BORROW 10 GRAND
JUST FOR A LITTLE WHILE?

11:44.570 --> 11:45.798
10 GRAND?

11:45.800 --> 11:47.461
WILL YOU HEAR ME OUT,
PLEASE?

11:47.470 --> 11:50.507
MY BOYFRIEND, DYLAN, SPOTTED ME
SOME CASH A FEW MONTHS AGO.

11:50.510 --> 11:54.298
NOW HE'S BUGGING ME ABOUT IT.
I CAN'T GET HIM OFF MY BACK.

11:54.310 --> 11:56.301
DID YOU TRY STANDING UP?

11:56.310 --> 11:59.404
THANKS.
I KNEW I COULD COUNT ON YOU.

11:59.410 --> 12:01.514
THIS AFTERNOON,
WE SHOULD POST AT PET STORES.

12:01.520 --> 12:04.080
PET OWNERS ARE MORE LIKELY
TO CALL WITH ANY TIPS.

12:04.090 --> 12:06.547
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

12:06.550 --> 12:07.551
HELLO?

12:07.560 --> 12:08.959
YES, I DID.

12:08.960 --> 12:12.282
OH, YOU HAVE?!

12:14.800 --> 12:15.824
WHAT HAPPENED?

12:15.830 --> 12:17.161
NOTHING.

12:17.170 --> 12:19.832
SOMEONE WAS JUST PLAYING
A STUPID TRICK.

12:19.840 --> 12:20.864
[ LAUGHTER ]

12:20.870 --> 12:22.337
[ BARKING ]

12:22.340 --> 12:25.366
LENNY SOFER. I HAD A CRUSH
ON HIM LAST YEAR.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.531
I PUT HIS PICTURE
IN MY LOCKER.

12:27.540 --> 12:30.202
I NEVER TOLD HIM,
BUT SOMEBODY DID.

12:30.210 --> 12:33.338
HE'S GONE OUT OF HIS WAY
TO BE MEAN TO ME EVER SINCE.

12:33.350 --> 12:37.116
OH, VERONICA, PLEASE DON'T WORRY
ABOUT IT. IT'S NOT WORTH IT.

12:37.120 --> 12:38.815
OH, IT'S SO WORTH IT.

12:38.820 --> 12:40.458
YOU PRAN K-CALL MAN DY?

12:40.460 --> 12:41.654
WHAT IF I DID?

12:41.660 --> 12:43.252
WELL, I WANT
TO SHAKE YOUR HAND.

12:43.260 --> 12:46.127
CONGRATULATIONS. YOU'VE BEEN
NAMED THE BIGGEST COCKROACH.

12:46.130 --> 12:47.688
THIS AWARD IS GIVEN
IN RECOGNITION

12:47.700 --> 12:49.998
OF YOUR UNPARALLELED LACK
OF DECENCY AND HUMANITY.

12:50.000 --> 12:52.719
BRAVO. YOU'RE GONNA DIE
FRIENDLESS AND ALONE.

12:52.730 --> 12:54.038
WHOA!
OOH!

12:54.040 --> 12:55.268
EVERYBODY KNOWS
YOU'RE THE BIGGEST --

12:55.270 --> 12:56.999
IF I WANT YOU
TO SPEAK,

12:57.010 --> 12:58.568
I'LL WAVE A SNAUSAGE
OVER YOUR NOSE.

12:58.570 --> 13:00.936
IF YOU USE MANDY AGAIN
TO TRY TO CONVINCE YOURSELF

13:00.940 --> 13:04.341
THAT YOU'RE NOT A LOSER,
I WILL RUIN YOUR LIFE -- GOT IT?

13:04.750 --> 13:05.774
YOU GOT IT?!

13:05.780 --> 13:07.475
OKAY, JEEZ.

13:10.250 --> 13:11.911
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU DID THAT.

13:11.920 --> 13:13.353
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU DIDN'T.

13:13.360 --> 13:15.510
YOU WANT PEOPLE
TO LEAVE YOU ALONE, MANDY,

13:15.520 --> 13:18.057
OR, BETTER YET,
TREAT YOU WITH RESPECT?

13:18.060 --> 13:19.948
DEMAND IT.
MAKE THEM.

13:26.700 --> 13:29.260
[ PANTING ]

13:29.270 --> 13:33.138
OH, HEY, BUDDY.
YOU WANT TO GO OUTSIDE?

13:33.140 --> 13:35.028
HEY.

13:35.040 --> 13:38.248
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

13:40.220 --> 13:41.312
Hello?

13:41.320 --> 13:43.686
VERONICA,
IT'S HANS AT THE POUND.

13:43.690 --> 13:45.544
I've got some bad news.

13:45.550 --> 13:49.714
ONE OF OUR GUYS FOUND CHESTER
BY THE SIDE OF THE HIGHWAY

13:49.720 --> 13:51.153
ON HIS WAY IN LAST NIGHT.

13:51.160 --> 13:52.821
HE'D BEEN HIT BY A CAR.

13:52.830 --> 13:54.957
THEY HAD TO PUT HIM DOWN.

14:01.200 --> 14:02.963
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
I FOUND THIS.

14:02.970 --> 14:06.337
I SAVED IT FOR YOU.

14:13.880 --> 14:16.849
[ SIGHS ]

14:20.120 --> 14:22.611
[ BIRDS CHIRPING,
WAVES CRASHING ]

14:31.430 --> 14:34.593
BACKUP AND I WALK BY HERE
ALMOST EVERY DAY.

14:34.600 --> 14:35.999
THIS USED TO BE COVERED

14:36.000 --> 14:38.662
WITH BAND FLIERS
AND SURFBOARDS FOR SALE.

14:38.670 --> 14:43.403
NOW EVERY INCH OF SPACE IS
COVERED WITH LOST-DOG NOTICES.

14:51.690 --> 14:55.080
HI, I WAS CALLING
ABOUT YOUR MISSING YORKIE.

14:55.090 --> 14:56.955
OH, YOU DID? GREAT.

14:56.960 --> 14:59.019
HOW DID YOU FIND HIM?

14:59.830 --> 15:01.957
THREE WEEKS?

15:01.960 --> 15:03.962
NO, I HAVEN'T SEEN HIM --

15:03.970 --> 15:05.926
JUST A CONCERNED DOG LOVER.

15:05.930 --> 15:08.262
HOW MUCH IS THE REWARD?

15:10.640 --> 15:12.130
HI, IS THIS BRIDGET?

15:12.140 --> 15:14.779
HI, I'M CALLING
ABOUT YOUR TOY SPANIEL, LOUIE.

15:14.780 --> 15:16.407
IS HE STILL MISSING?

15:16.410 --> 15:19.402
I'LL DEFINITELY BE ON
THE LOOKOUT FOR HIM. GOOD LUCK.

15:25.690 --> 15:28.181
ONLY THE OWNERS
WHO HAVE OFFERED BIG REWARDS

15:28.190 --> 15:29.987
HAVE GOTTEN THEIR DOGS BACK.

15:29.990 --> 15:32.129
WHAT HAPPENS TO DOGS WHO DON'T
BRING A HIGH-ENOUGH PRICE?

15:32.130 --> 15:36.692
DO THEY END UP LIKE CHESTER --
LEI-T BY THE HIGHWAY TO DIE?

15:42.800 --> 15:44.336
I CAN'T DO ANYTHING FOR MANDY,

15:44.340 --> 15:46.604
BUT IF SOMEONE IS STEALING DOGS
IN NEPTUNE,

15:46.610 --> 15:48.601
THEY NEED
TO BE BROUGHT DOWN HARD,

15:48.610 --> 15:50.749
THEN BEATEN
WITH SOME SORT OF TIRE IRON

15:50.750 --> 15:54.311
AND DUMPED
INTO THE NEAREST BODY OF WATER.

15:54.320 --> 15:57.414
WHAT DID YOU SAY
TO DUNCAN?

15:57.420 --> 15:58.614
WHERE IS HE?

15:58.620 --> 16:00.053
EXCUSE ME?

16:00.060 --> 16:01.618
I THINK YOU KNOW
WHY HE LEI-T.

16:01.620 --> 16:03.986
IN FACT, YOU'RE PROBABLY
THE REASON HE LEI-T.

16:03.990 --> 16:06.322
WHAT DID YOU SAY TO HIM,
VERONICA?

16:07.230 --> 16:09.448
LET'S START
WITH WHAT I DIDN'T TELL HIM.

16:09.460 --> 16:12.861
I DIDN'T TELL HIM THAT HIS
MOTHER THREATENED TO KILL ME.

16:12.870 --> 16:14.394
I DIDN'T TELL HIM

16:14.400 --> 16:16.493
THAT HIS MOTHER
DROVE MY MOTHER OUT OF TOWN.

16:16.500 --> 16:20.539
I KNOW YOU THINK I HATE YOU,
BUT I DON'T.

16:20.540 --> 16:24.249
I JUST CAN'T STAND
TO LOOK AT YOU.

16:24.250 --> 16:25.979
EVERY TIME I SEE YOU,

16:25.980 --> 16:29.643
I SEE EVERYTHING THAT'S WRONG
IN MY LIFE, IN MY FAMILY.

16:29.650 --> 16:31.709
I SEE
MY HUSBAND'S INFIDELITY

16:31.720 --> 16:35.019
AND YOUR MOTHER IN HIS OFFICE,
IN HIS HOTEL ROOM.

16:35.020 --> 16:37.580
I SEE YOUR FATHER
TRYING TO DESTROY US!

16:37.590 --> 16:40.252
THEN WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

16:42.660 --> 16:45.299
I NEEDED TO ASK YOUR DAUGHTER
A FEW QUESTIONS.

16:45.300 --> 16:48.269
YOU DON'T NEED TO ASK HER
ANYTHING. JUST LEAVE HER ALONE.

16:48.270 --> 16:50.101
YOU DON'T SCARE ME, KEITH.

16:50.110 --> 16:52.533
IF YOU WERE
SUCH A GREAT DETECTIVE,

16:52.540 --> 16:55.236
YOU WOULD HAVE SEEN
WHAT WAS GOING ON

16:55.240 --> 16:57.777
RIGHT UNDERNEATH YOUR NOSE.

17:00.280 --> 17:03.488
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

17:09.490 --> 17:10.286
WAIT.

17:10.290 --> 17:12.019
I'LL HELP YOU FIND DUNCAN

17:12.030 --> 17:14.624
IF YOU DROP THE CHARGES
AGAINST WEEVIL.

17:14.630 --> 17:18.566
YOU WANT THE INTRUDER CAUGHT
IN LILLY'S BEDROOM RELEASED?

17:18.570 --> 17:21.596
I'M SURE I SHOULD BE SURPRISED,
BUT I'M NOT.

17:21.600 --> 17:23.864
NOTHING WAS STOLEN.
NOTHING WAS DAMAGED.

17:23.870 --> 17:27.772
I MIGHT HAVE AN IDEA WHERE
DUNCAN WENT. THAT'S MY OFFER.

17:32.910 --> 17:34.468
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

17:34.480 --> 17:36.914
TRUTH IS, I HAVE NO IDEA
WHERE DUNCAN MIGHT BE,

17:36.920 --> 17:38.387
BUT SHE DOESN'T KNOW THAT.

17:38.390 --> 17:40.984
AS FOR THE WHEREABOUTS
OF LOST DOGS,

17:40.990 --> 17:42.514
LET'S SEE WHO BITES

17:42.520 --> 17:45.387
WHEN I INCREASE THE REWARD
EXPONENTIALLY.

17:49.500 --> 17:51.661
IS DAD STILL AT DINNER?

17:51.670 --> 17:52.819
YEAH.

17:52.830 --> 17:55.230
BUT HE'S NOT FAR --
I'M SURE IF YOU TRIED,

17:55.240 --> 17:58.437
YOU COULD BLOW SMOKE
UP HIS ASS FROM HERE.

17:59.440 --> 18:01.374
HEY, TRIN,
IF YOU TAKE YOUR TOP OFF

18:01.380 --> 18:03.439
BEFORE YOU GET
ON THE MECHANICAL BULL,

18:03.450 --> 18:05.145
YOU WON'T FALL OFF.

18:08.420 --> 18:10.069
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

18:10.080 --> 18:11.308
NOTHING.

18:12.290 --> 18:16.351
DON'T YOU HAVE SOME HOMEWORK
TO DO, LITTLE BROTHER?

18:18.560 --> 18:22.257
DID THAT WANNABE-PRODUCER
BOYFRIEND DO THIS TO YOU?

18:24.100 --> 18:26.819
WHAT'S HIS NAME --
DYLAN?

18:26.830 --> 18:27.990
WHAT'S HIS LAST NAME?

18:28.000 --> 18:29.467
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

18:29.470 --> 18:30.960
IT DOES NOW!
TELL ME!

18:30.970 --> 18:32.369
YOU'VE MADE IT CLEAR

18:32.370 --> 18:36.238
THAT YOU HAVE NO INTEREST
IN MY PROBLEMS, LOGAN.

18:36.240 --> 18:37.673
DON'T BE WISHY-WASHY.

18:37.680 --> 18:40.615
IT'S SO UNATTRACT IVE
IN A GUY.

18:45.920 --> 18:49.583
I WALKED IN ON THEM MAKING OUT
ON THE COUCH LAST NIGHT.

18:49.590 --> 18:51.421
SHE WAS SITTING
ON HIS LAP.

18:51.430 --> 18:54.957
HEY! NO DISCUSSING PARENTAL PDA
AT LUNCH! IT'S YOUR RULE!

18:54.960 --> 18:58.669
SORRY. I CAN'T BE THE ONLY ONE
WITH THAT BURNED IN MY BRAIN.

18:58.670 --> 18:59.898
I HAD TO SHARE.

18:59.900 --> 19:03.506
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

19:03.510 --> 19:04.966
HELLO?

19:04.970 --> 19:06.767
YES, THIS IS BRIDGET.

19:06.770 --> 19:09.170
[ GASPS ] WONDERFUL!

19:09.180 --> 19:13.446
YES, THE REWARD IS
STILL $1,000.

19:13.450 --> 19:16.544
HOW ABOUT THIS AI-TERNOON?

19:16.550 --> 19:17.517
GREAT.

19:17.520 --> 19:20.819
I'LL SEND...MY BROTHER
TO MEET YOU.

19:20.820 --> 19:22.913
DOG BEACH, 3:00.

19:22.920 --> 19:24.581
THAN KS.

19:24.590 --> 19:25.454
BYE-BYE.

19:25.460 --> 19:26.779
SO, I'M YOUR BROTHER?

19:26.790 --> 19:28.451
I DIDN'T MEAN "BROTHER"
LIKE "BROTHER."

19:28.460 --> 19:30.667
I MEANT "BROTHER" LIKE...

19:30.670 --> 19:31.659
YOU KNOW.

19:31.670 --> 19:34.389
[ LAUGHS ]
YEAH, I KNOW.

19:34.400 --> 19:36.197
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA GET
1,000 BUCKS?

19:36.200 --> 19:37.633
IF YOU'RE ROLLING
LIKE THAT,

19:37.640 --> 19:39.528
YOU'VE BEEN HOLDING OUT
ON A BROTHER.

19:39.540 --> 19:43.874
[ BIRDS CHIRPING,
WAVES CRASHING ]

20:06.770 --> 20:08.635
[ Hispanic accent]
YOU LOST DOG?

20:08.640 --> 20:11.006
I SURE DID.
HI, THERE, LOUIE.

20:11.010 --> 20:12.705
HOW YOU DOING, BOY?

20:12.710 --> 20:14.405
I MISSED YOU.

20:14.410 --> 20:15.638
YES, I DID.

20:15.640 --> 20:18.905
WHERE WAS HE?
HOW'D YOU FIND HIM?

20:18.910 --> 20:20.571
NO HABLO INGLS.

20:20.580 --> 20:22.775
OH.

20:22.780 --> 20:25.317
ALL RIGHT, THEN.

20:27.620 --> 20:29.281
THAN KS, MAN.
GRACIAS.

20:29.290 --> 20:31.485
COME ON.

20:32.930 --> 20:35.353
[ BARKING ]

20:36.700 --> 20:37.792
OH, NO!

20:37.800 --> 20:38.926
AAAH! AAAH!

20:38.930 --> 20:41.694
AAAAAAAAH!

20:41.700 --> 20:43.861
[ GROWLING ]

20:43.870 --> 20:45.235
AAAH! AAH! AAAH!

20:45.240 --> 20:48.937
I'M SO SORRY!
I'M SO SORRY!

20:48.940 --> 20:53.513
MY-MY ZAPATO!
MY SHOE!

20:53.520 --> 20:54.669
AAH!

20:54.680 --> 20:57.069
HE JUST RAN FROM ME.
THAT'S SO WEIRD.

20:57.080 --> 20:58.741
EL LOCO PERRO.

20:58.750 --> 21:00.479
SORRY.

21:09.160 --> 21:10.696
TAG. YOU'RE IT.

21:10.700 --> 21:13.897
NOW ITS TIME TO PLAY
"FOLLOW THE DOG THIEF."

21:13.900 --> 21:17.267
HMM...YOU'RE WALKING.

21:33.190 --> 21:35.715
[ MAN SPEAKING SPANISH ]

21:51.470 --> 21:53.472
YOU! YOU!

21:53.480 --> 21:56.301
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:02.080 --> 22:03.718
OH, CRAP.

22:07.050 --> 22:08.688
ME DINERO!
NO, NO.
YOU STOLE THE DOG.

22:08.690 --> 22:11.056
I NO STEAL!
NO, I NO STEAL!

22:11.060 --> 22:13.051
[ MEN SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:13.060 --> 22:14.755
[ BARKS ]

22:14.760 --> 22:18.218
AND IT'S TIME FOR THE
INTERNATIONAL LANGUAGE OF...

22:18.230 --> 22:20.323
[ HORN BLARES ]

22:21.940 --> 22:25.467
OKAY, NOW,
WHO STOLE THE DOG?

22:26.770 --> 22:28.237
EL HOMBRE DE LOS PERROS!

22:28.240 --> 22:30.447
EL HOMBRE DE LOS PERROS!

22:30.450 --> 22:32.475
A DOG MAN?

22:32.480 --> 22:34.619
DOES HE DRIVE A WHITE VAN?
DO YOU KNOW HIM?

22:34.620 --> 22:37.748
S, WHITE VAN.
EL HOMBRE DE LOS PERROS...

22:37.750 --> 22:40.913
DO YOU KNOW HIS NAME?

22:40.920 --> 22:42.512
SU NOMBRE?

22:42.520 --> 22:43.885
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:46.030 --> 22:47.554
[ LAUGHTER ]

22:47.560 --> 22:50.620
SURE, LET'S PLAY DIRTY CHARADES
WITH THE GRINGA.

22:50.630 --> 22:52.427
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:52.430 --> 22:53.533
[ LAUGHTER ]

22:53.540 --> 22:54.962
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:54.970 --> 22:58.007
OKAY, UH...
MUCHOS GRACIAS.

22:58.010 --> 22:59.568
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

22:59.570 --> 23:01.379
19%:
gs:

23:01.380 --> 23:04.076
SO THERE'S A DOG MAN WHO HIRES
THESE GUYS TO RETURN DOGS.

23:04.080 --> 23:06.605
HE DRIVES A WHITE VAN
OR MAYBE A WHITE HORSE,

23:06.610 --> 23:09.818
AND HE LIKES
TO SPANK BUSTY WOMEN.

23:09.820 --> 23:13.517
BASICALLY, THAT'S ANY MALE
LIVING IN NEPTUNE.

23:17.990 --> 23:19.184
[ LOUIE BARKS ]

23:19.190 --> 23:20.691
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

23:20.700 --> 23:22.190
COME ON, LOUIE.

23:22.200 --> 23:25.522
ALL RIGHT, NOW, PLEASE,
BE HOT, GRATEFUL, SINGLE.

23:25.530 --> 23:28.169
HI. I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU LOST LOUIE.

23:28.170 --> 23:30.468
OH, YOU FOUND HIM!

23:30.470 --> 23:32.006
I SURE DID.

23:32.010 --> 23:33.500
OHHH.

23:45.220 --> 23:47.757
HELLO, LADIES.

24:05.940 --> 24:07.874
WHAT THE --
YOU KILL DOGS?

24:07.880 --> 24:10.872
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN MY VAN?
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

24:10.880 --> 24:13.713
YOU'RE KIDNAPPING 09er DOGS,
HOLDING THEM AT THE POUND,

24:13.720 --> 24:17.269
AND WAITING FOR AN OFFER
OF A BIG REWARD?

24:17.280 --> 24:20.181
YOU BREAK INTO MY VAN, AND
YOU'RE ACCUSING ME OF STEALING?

24:20.190 --> 24:22.408
SO WHEN MANDY AND I
CAME LOOKING FOR CHESTER,

24:22.420 --> 24:25.878
YOU REALIZED YOU SCREWED UP --
DOGNAPPED FROM A POOR GIRL.

24:25.890 --> 24:29.621
SO YOU CUT YOUR LOSSES AND THREW
HIM TO THE SIDE OF THE ROAD?

24:29.630 --> 24:31.860
ACTUALLY,
I ROUNDED UP 101 OF THEM,

24:31.870 --> 24:34.532
AND SOME CRAZY LADY
IS MAKING A COAT.

24:37.640 --> 24:39.460
HOW OLD ARE YOU,
ANYWAY, HANS?

24:39.470 --> 24:41.836
18. WHY?

24:42.480 --> 24:44.243
COMMUNITY SOAP.

24:48.020 --> 24:51.512
ALWAYS GETTING OUT THE BACK
OF SOME DUDE'S VAN, AREN'T YOU?

24:51.520 --> 24:53.215
YOU'RE OUT.

24:53.220 --> 24:56.553
HOW MANY "GET OUT OF JAIL FREE"
CARDS DO YOU HAVE, ANYWAY?

24:56.560 --> 24:58.551
I'M PRETTY SURE
THAT WAS MY LAST,

24:58.560 --> 25:00.596
SO KEEP YOUR FELONIES
TO A MINIMUM.

25:00.600 --> 25:02.056
I AM WHAT I AM.

25:02.060 --> 25:06.019
A LEOPARD'S SPOTS --
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY SAY.

25:11.140 --> 25:12.539
HI.

25:12.540 --> 25:14.076
HEY, I NEED YOUR HELP.

25:14.080 --> 25:16.901
WOULD IT BE WEIRD FOR ME
TO START MY OWN DRINKING GAME --

25:16.910 --> 25:19.049
DO A SHOT EVERY TIME
SOMEONE ASKS FOR HELP?

25:19.050 --> 25:22.577
I NEED YOU TO TRACK DOWN TRINA'S
LEECH-OF-THE-WEEK BOYFRIEND.

25:22.580 --> 25:24.741
WHAT'D HE DO?
HE BEAT HER UP.

25:24.750 --> 25:27.082
I PLAN ON RETURNING
THE FAVOR.

25:27.090 --> 25:29.081
ALL I KNOW
IS HIS FIRST NAME -- DYLAN.

25:29.090 --> 25:31.888
AND HE'S PRODUCING
THIS STEAMER.

25:34.100 --> 25:35.192
EASY.

25:37.530 --> 25:39.191
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

25:40.430 --> 25:41.567
HEY.

25:41.570 --> 25:43.561
GOING OUT?

25:43.570 --> 25:45.162
OH, NOT AT THE MOMENT.

25:45.170 --> 25:49.504
BUT JUST IN CASE,
GOTTA HAVE THE GAME FACE ON.

25:49.510 --> 25:53.549
CAMERA'S PRYING EYES
ARE NEVER FAR AWAY.

25:53.550 --> 25:54.915
HMM.

25:54.920 --> 25:57.741
HEY, WHAT DO YOU FEEL LIKE
FOR DINNER?

25:57.750 --> 25:59.741
I THINK I'M GONNA COOK.

25:59.750 --> 26:03.550
YEAH...
I'M NOT REALLY HUNGRY.

26:03.560 --> 26:04.720
ARE YOU OKAY?

26:04.730 --> 26:07.449
JUST BOYFRIEND STUFF.

26:07.460 --> 26:08.893
NO BIG DEAL.

26:08.900 --> 26:11.619
YOU KNOW, EVEN IF IT'S
A SMALL DEAL, I'M --

26:11.630 --> 26:13.564
YOU CAN ALWAYS
TALK TO ME ABOUT IT.

26:13.570 --> 26:17.904
WELL, I SORT OF GOT HIS HOPES UP
ABOUT YOU DOING HIS MOVIE,

26:17.910 --> 26:21.801
AND NOW THE FINANCING IS FALLING
THROUGH, AND HE'S FREAKING OUT.

26:21.810 --> 26:23.869
TRINA,
YOU GOT TO TALK TO ME

26:23.880 --> 26:26.644
BEFORE YOU GO MAKING PROMISES
TO ANYBODY.

26:26.650 --> 26:28.811
DAD, I SO DON'T CARE
ABOUT DYLAN.

26:28.820 --> 26:30.981
THIS IS ME
THINKING ABOUT YOU.

26:30.990 --> 26:34.016
THIS IS A CAREER-DEFINING MOMENT
YOU'RE PASSING UP.

26:34.020 --> 26:38.184
I MEAN, HELLO!
TRAVOLTA -- "PULP FICTION."

26:38.190 --> 26:39.350
REALLY?

26:39.360 --> 26:41.499
IT'S THAT GOOD?

26:41.500 --> 26:43.866
IT'S BETTER
THAN "THAT GOOD."

26:45.430 --> 26:49.161
WELL, I GUESS I'D BETTER
HEAR ABOUT IT, THEN.

26:49.170 --> 26:52.662
WHY DON'T YOU HAVE
YOUR BOYFRIEND COME BY LATER.

26:52.670 --> 26:54.604
[ SIGHS ]

26:54.610 --> 26:57.431
THANK YOU SO MUCH,
DADDY!

26:57.440 --> 27:01.718
Veronica: HI, I'M CALLING FROM
TODD RUSSELL'S OFFICE AT C.A.A.

27:01.720 --> 27:03.813
HE READ YOUR SCRIPT,
"ESCAPING YOUR PAST,"

27:03.820 --> 27:06.288
AND HE WENT NUTS OVER IT.

27:06.290 --> 27:08.110
HAVE YOU SOLD IT YET?

27:08.120 --> 27:10.281
REALLY?

27:10.290 --> 27:13.282
WHO'S PRODUCING IT?

27:13.290 --> 27:16.054
IS THAT "G-O-R-A-N"?

27:16.060 --> 27:19.063
GREAT. I'M SURE HE'LL WANT
TO SPEAK WITH HIM.

27:19.070 --> 27:21.664
MAYBE WE CAN GET YOU GUYS
A DEAL.

27:21.670 --> 27:24.537
OKAY, WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.

27:24.540 --> 27:26.303
THAN KS. BYE.

27:28.540 --> 27:30.201
DYLAN GORAN.

27:30.210 --> 27:33.441
IS THERE REALLY AN AGENT NAMED
"TODD RUSSELL" AT C.A.A.?

27:33.450 --> 27:36.044
THERE COULD BE.
MAYBE.

27:39.050 --> 27:43.180
LOOKS LIKE TRINA'S ROMEO
HAS HAD TROUBLE WITH THE LADIES.

27:43.190 --> 27:46.455
TWO WOMEN HAVE FILED
RESTRAINING ORDERS AGAINST HIM

27:46.460 --> 27:48.928
IN THE LAST FIVE YEARS.

27:53.200 --> 27:55.964
DAD. HEY, I NEED TRINA.
IT'S IMPORTANT.

27:55.970 --> 27:58.109
OH, HEY, SON.
SHE'S IN THE SHOWER.

27:58.110 --> 28:01.705
HER BOYFRIEND'S COMING OVER
TO PITCH ME A PART IN HIS MOVIE.

28:01.710 --> 28:03.234
AREN'T YOU RETIRED?

28:03.240 --> 28:05.640
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
RECONNECTING WITH YOUR FAMILY.

28:05.650 --> 28:07.003
TRINA IS FAMILY.

28:07.010 --> 28:09.672
I'M HELPING HER OUT.
IT'S WHAT DADS DO.

28:09.680 --> 28:12.148
No, listen,
Trina's boyfriend --

28:12.150 --> 28:13.879
[ BEEP ]

28:16.620 --> 28:18.850
DYLAN'S ON HIS WAY
TO THE HOUSE.

28:18.860 --> 28:22.318
AND DAD'S COOKING
FOR HIM.

28:26.730 --> 28:30.564
DAD,
THIS IS DYLAN GORAN.

28:30.570 --> 28:32.868
DYLAN, MY FATHER --
AARON ECHOLLS.

28:32.870 --> 28:35.031
MR. ECHOLLS.
IT'S A PLEASURE.

28:35.040 --> 28:37.770
I'M SO GLAD
YOU DECIDED TO MEET.

28:37.780 --> 28:40.704
PLEASE, CALL ME "AARON."

28:43.220 --> 28:44.289
HEY...

28:44.290 --> 28:46.884
TASTE THIS FOR ME,
WILL YOU?

28:50.220 --> 28:52.654
MM-MMM!

28:52.660 --> 28:54.150
PERFECT.

28:55.460 --> 28:56.859
NAH, NOT QUITE.

28:56.860 --> 28:59.897
SO, DYLAN...

28:59.900 --> 29:01.458
TELL ME ABOUT THIS PART.

29:01.470 --> 29:05.304
YOU'D BE PLAYING A HIT MAN --
A JUNKIE HIT MAN.

29:05.310 --> 29:08.575
IT'S ONLY TWO DAYS OF WORK --
YOU'D BE IN AND OUT.

29:08.580 --> 29:12.471
IF YOU SAID "YES,"
THEY'D HAVE A GREEN LIGHT.

29:12.480 --> 29:13.913
HMM.

29:14.680 --> 29:18.946
A STRUNG-OUT HIT MAN, HUH?

29:18.950 --> 29:20.281
WITH A CONSCIENCE.

29:20.290 --> 29:22.850
HE'S ON THE JUNK
BECAUSE HE'S TORMENTED.

29:22.860 --> 29:26.887
IT'S THE ONLY WAY HE CAN GET OUT
OF HIS HEAD -- ESCAPE THE PAIN.

29:26.890 --> 29:31.827
YOU KNOW...IT SOUNDS A LOT
LIKE MY OLD MAN.

29:31.830 --> 29:33.525
HE USED TO BEAT ME
AND MY MOM

29:33.530 --> 29:37.660
AND THEN...TRY TO DRINK
THE DEMONS AWAY.

29:37.670 --> 29:41.037
YEAH, YEAH.
IT'S A LOT LIKE THAT.

29:41.040 --> 29:43.634
YOU COULD DEFINITELY
DRAW FROM THAT.

29:43.640 --> 29:46.347
YEAH.

29:46.350 --> 29:48.113
OH, MAN.

29:48.120 --> 29:50.941
HE USED TO BEAT MY MOM
TILL SHE PASSED OUT.

29:50.950 --> 29:53.145
SHE'D CAKE MAKEUP
ALL OVER HER FACE,

29:53.150 --> 29:55.653
WEAR DARK GLASSES
AROUND THE HOUSE,

29:55.660 --> 29:58.652
BUT YOU KNOW, I COULD ALWAYS
RECOGNIZE THE SIGNS.

29:58.660 --> 30:01.697
FINALLY, I GOT THE COURAGE UP
TO TRY AND STOP HIM.

30:01.700 --> 30:04.669
BUT, I MEAN, I'M JUST
A SCRAWNY LITTLE KID --

30:04.670 --> 30:08.128
HE'S BUILT LIKE A WALL.

30:09.500 --> 30:12.606
HE PUT A CIGARETTE OUT
ON MY HAND

30:12.610 --> 30:14.134
AND SAID, "NICE TRY, KID."

30:14.140 --> 30:17.371
YOU KNOW, YOU CAN STILL
SEE THE SCARS.

30:17.380 --> 30:18.369
LOOK.

30:18.380 --> 30:20.177
WOW. [ LAUGHS ]

30:20.180 --> 30:22.171
YOU SEE THEM THERE?

30:22.180 --> 30:23.249
UH...

30:23.250 --> 30:24.786
NO, I DON'T.

30:24.790 --> 30:28.112
COME ON, IT'S RIGHT THERE,
RIGHT THERE.

30:28.660 --> 30:29.888
DADDY!

30:29.890 --> 30:31.528
YOU THINK YOU CAN HIT
MY DAUGHTER?

30:31.530 --> 30:32.781
DADDY, NO!

30:32.790 --> 30:34.496
MY DAUGHTER!

30:34.500 --> 30:38.391
* WHEN THE MOON HITS YOUR EYE
LIKE A BIG PIZZA PIE *

30:38.400 --> 30:40.265
* THAT'S AMOR *

30:40.270 --> 30:41.362
DADDY, STOP!

30:42.200 --> 30:47.706
* WHEN THE WORLD SEEMS TO SHINE
LIKE YOU'VE HAD TOO MUCH WINE *

30:47.710 --> 30:49.268
* THAT'S AMOR *

30:49.280 --> 30:50.304
DADDY!

30:52.050 --> 30:54.814
* BELLS WILL RING
TING-A-LING-A-LING *

30:54.820 --> 30:56.014
* TING-A-LING-A-LING *

30:56.020 --> 30:59.512
* AND YOU'LL SING VITA BELLA *

30:59.520 --> 31:00.817
DADDY, NO!

31:01.660 --> 31:04.220
* HEARTS WILL PLAY
TIPPI-TIPPI-TAY *

31:04.230 --> 31:09.998
* TIPPI-TIPPI-TAY
LIKE A GAY TARANTELLA *

31:10.630 --> 31:15.431
* WHEN THE STARS MAKE YOUR DROOL
JUST-A LIKE PASTA FAZOOL *

31:15.440 --> 31:18.307
* THAT'S AMOR *

31:20.610 --> 31:22.373
DADDY, NO!

31:22.380 --> 31:25.543
* WHEN YOU DANCE DOWN THE STREET
WITH A CLOUD AT YOUR FEET *

31:25.550 --> 31:27.506
* YOU'RE IN LOVE *

31:28.650 --> 31:30.743
OH, HEY, SON.

31:30.750 --> 31:32.615
HOW WAS SCHOOL?

31:35.460 --> 31:36.256
UHH...

31:36.260 --> 31:37.852
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT?

31:37.860 --> 31:42.251
I CONSIDERED YOUR OFFER,
BUT I THINK I'M GONNA PASS.

31:43.700 --> 31:45.327
LOGAN...

31:45.330 --> 31:47.992
CAN YOU SEE THIS YOUNG MAN
TO HIS CAR, PLEASE?

31:48.000 --> 31:49.763
I'D BE HAPPY TO.

31:49.770 --> 31:52.068
* SCUSA ME, BUT YOU SEE *

31:52.070 --> 31:57.235
* BACK IN OLD NAPOLI,
THAT'S AMOR *

31:59.480 --> 32:00.469
WOW.

32:00.480 --> 32:02.368
FATHER KNOWS BEST.

32:06.550 --> 32:10.384
DID YOU THINK
LILLY LOVED WEEVIL?

32:12.690 --> 32:14.248
I DON'T KNOW.

32:14.260 --> 32:19.618
UM...LILLY NEVER MENTIONED
ANYTHING TO ME ABOUT WEEVIL.

32:19.630 --> 32:23.168
I WAS WONDERING WHEN YOU WERE
GONNA ASK ME ABOUT THAT.

32:23.170 --> 32:25.434
YEAH, WELL...
[ SIGHS ] I DON'T KNOW.

32:25.440 --> 32:28.932
WHEN HE'S CAUGHT IN HER BEDROOM,
I GUESS YOU GOT TO THINK.

32:28.940 --> 32:32.000
YOU'RE HANDLING IT A LOT BETTER
THAN I THOUGHT YOU WOULD.

32:32.010 --> 32:35.116
I LOVED LILLY.

32:35.120 --> 32:37.714
AND LILLY LOVED GUYS.

32:37.720 --> 32:39.244
LOGAN, YOU KNOW THAT --

32:39.250 --> 32:41.718
NO, SHE USED TO SAY THAT HER --
[CLEARS THROAT]

32:41.720 --> 32:44.848
HER PARENTS WORSHIPED DUNCAN
AND TOLERATED HER.

32:44.860 --> 32:46.555
AND IF SHE COULDN'T
PLEASE THEM,

32:46.560 --> 32:50.155
SHE WAS GONNA GO OUT OF HER WAY
TO PISS THEM OFF.

32:50.160 --> 32:54.392
WEEVIL MUST HAVE BEEN
PERFECT FOR THAT.

32:54.400 --> 32:56.834
I KNOW LILLY LOVED YOU.

32:56.840 --> 33:00.662
JUST NOT LIKE I LOVED HER.

33:00.670 --> 33:03.207
IT'S OKAY.

33:03.210 --> 33:06.202
NO, YOU KNOW,
IT KIND OF LETS ME OFF THE HOOK.

33:06.210 --> 33:09.611
YOU KNOW, I DON'T HAVE TO FEEL
GUILTY ANYMORE.

33:10.850 --> 33:13.683
FEEL GUILTY ABOUT WHAT?

33:15.660 --> 33:17.514
MOVING ON.

33:33.870 --> 33:35.770
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

33:35.780 --> 33:37.475
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

33:37.480 --> 33:38.549
NO IDEA.

33:43.120 --> 33:44.985
WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT THIS.

33:44.990 --> 33:46.389
I KNOW.
[ LAUGHS ]

33:46.390 --> 33:49.587
MAYBE WE SHOULD KEEP IT
TO OURSELVES FOR A WHILE

33:49.590 --> 33:50.784
AND SEE WHAT HAPPENS.

33:50.790 --> 33:52.189
MEET IN MOP CLOSETS.

33:52.190 --> 33:55.227
PASS EACH OTHER SECRET NOTES
IN THE HALLWAY.

33:57.800 --> 34:02.191
COME ON, I'LL DRIVE YOU HOME
ON THE BACKSTREETS.

34:12.150 --> 34:14.869
[ LAUGHS ]

34:14.880 --> 34:19.681
OH, MY GOSH, LOOK WHAT I FOUND
IN MY CEREAL BOX THIS MORNING.

34:19.690 --> 34:21.487
IT'S A SPY PEN!

34:21.490 --> 34:22.309
OOH.

34:22.320 --> 34:24.982
WHAT'S A SPY PEN?

34:24.990 --> 34:27.049
HOW COVERT OPS OF YOU!

34:27.060 --> 34:30.655
I'M GONNA USE IT TO PASS
SECRET MESSAGES TO MY LOVERS.

34:30.660 --> 34:33.197
THIS IS GOING TO BE
A VERY BUSY PEN.

34:33.200 --> 34:35.088
[ LAUGHS ]

34:35.100 --> 34:37.091
YOU OKAY?

34:40.110 --> 34:42.203
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

34:47.510 --> 34:48.738
HI.

34:48.750 --> 34:50.342
HI.

34:50.350 --> 34:53.080
I'M GOING TO THE CITY POUND
TONIGHT. YOU WANT TO COME WITH?

34:53.090 --> 34:54.580
WHAT? WHY?

34:54.590 --> 34:57.184
I BELIEVE THAT GUY HANS
AND THOSE GUYS FROM THE POUND

34:57.190 --> 34:59.681
ARE DOGNAPPING PUREBRED DOGS
FROM THE 09er ZIP

34:59.690 --> 35:02.625
AND HOLDING THEM THERE
UNTIL THE OWNERS OFFER REWARDS.

35:02.630 --> 35:06.361
DO YOU THINK THERE'S A CHANCE
CHESTER MIGHT STILL BE THERE?

35:06.370 --> 35:08.258
I WOULDN'T GET MY HOPES UP.

35:08.270 --> 35:09.532
LISTEN, IT'S STU PI D,

35:09.540 --> 35:11.861
AND IF YOU DON'T WANT
ANY PART --

35:11.870 --> 35:13.167
I'M IN.

35:16.780 --> 35:19.999
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

35:20.010 --> 35:21.216
ME?

35:21.220 --> 35:22.847
FINALLY -- ME.

35:22.850 --> 35:26.217
I CAN'T DATE YOU ANYMORE.

35:27.890 --> 35:29.118
HUH.

35:30.620 --> 35:32.679
WHOA. OKAY.

35:32.690 --> 35:34.749
TRUST ME,
YOU DON'T WANT TO DATE ME.

35:34.760 --> 35:36.648
I'M A TRAIN WRECK,
SERIOUSLY.

35:36.660 --> 35:39.697
THE FIRST GUY I LOVED DROPPED
OFF THE FACE OF THE EARTH --

35:39.700 --> 35:41.839
PROBABLY BECAUSE
OF SOMETHING I SAID.

35:41.840 --> 35:44.968
AND THE LAST GUY I DATED
TURNED OUT TO BE A DRUG DEALER.

35:44.970 --> 35:48.508
AND I JUST MADE OUT WITH
MY DEAD BEST FRIEND'S BOYFRIEND,

35:48.510 --> 35:50.239
WHO, INCIDENTALLY, I HATE.

35:50.240 --> 35:53.903
SO. . .TRAIN WRECK.

35:55.520 --> 35:57.818
BUT...LEO,
YOU ARE THE SWEETEST --

35:57.820 --> 36:01.711
PLEASE, DON'T TELL ME
HOW SWEET I AM.

36:01.720 --> 36:03.881
WELL,
YOU'RE ALSO SERIOUSLY HOT,

36:03.890 --> 36:06.723
SO YOU'LL BE SINGLE
FOR ABOUT 3 SECONDS.

36:06.730 --> 36:09.597
SEE, NOW,
THAT'S MORE HELPFUL.

36:09.600 --> 36:13.024
I'M SORRY TO DUMP THIS
ON YOU. I JUST...

36:14.200 --> 36:18.603
I GENUINELY CARE ABOUT YOU,
AND I WANTED TO BE HONEST.

36:18.610 --> 36:22.034
SO, MY RESPONSE
IS SUPPOSED TO BE WHAT --

36:22.040 --> 36:23.439
"THAN KS"?

36:23.440 --> 36:26.671
PROBABLY OVERSHOOTING
A BIT, HUH?

36:26.680 --> 36:28.409
[ LAUGHS ]

36:28.420 --> 36:31.617
YOU COULD TELL ME
THAT YOU UNDERSTAND.

36:31.620 --> 36:36.410
AND...THAT...
WE CAN STILL BE FRIENDS.

36:37.290 --> 36:39.019
THAT WOULD BE COOL.

36:39.030 --> 36:42.329
'CAUSE I NEED TO FOLLOW
THIS CONFESSION

36:42.330 --> 36:44.321
BY ASKING FOR A FAVOR.

36:45.970 --> 36:48.336
[ LAUGHS ]

36:48.340 --> 36:49.659
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

36:49.670 --> 36:52.104
OPEN UP!
SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT!

36:52.110 --> 36:53.737
[ DOGS BARKING ]

36:55.410 --> 36:57.230
WE NEED TO TAKE
A LOOK AROUND.

36:57.240 --> 36:59.208
LOOK,
HER DOG'S NOT HERE!

36:59.210 --> 37:00.768
TAKE US TO THE BACK --
NOW.

37:00.780 --> 37:02.543
YOU WANT TO SHOW ME
A WARRANT?

37:02.550 --> 37:04.040
THIS IS
A PUBLIC COUNTY BUILDING.

37:04.050 --> 37:07.110
YOU'RE A COUNTY EMPLOYEE.
I'M A COUNTY DEPUTY SHERIFF.

37:07.120 --> 37:09.054
DON'T MAKE ME WAKE UP
A JUDGE.

37:09.060 --> 37:10.254
[ SIGHS ]

37:10.260 --> 37:12.251
COME ON.

37:12.260 --> 37:15.229
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

37:16.530 --> 37:20.728
JUST LIKE YOU WERE TOLD, MISSY,
YOUR DOG'S DEAD.

37:20.730 --> 37:21.731
HE'S NOT HERE.

37:21.740 --> 37:24.129
WELL,
WHAT'S IN THIS ROOM HERE?

37:24.140 --> 37:26.233
WHAT'S IN THAT ROOM?

37:26.240 --> 37:27.730
IT'S LOCKED.

37:27.740 --> 37:29.879
IT'S WHERE WE KEEP DOGS
WITH CONTAGIOUS DISEASES.

37:29.880 --> 37:32.440
YOU GO IN THERE,
YOU CAN INFECT OTHER --

37:32.450 --> 37:33.906
WE'LL RISK IT.

37:37.380 --> 37:39.018
YOUR DOG'S NOT IN THERE.

37:44.120 --> 37:47.248
WELL, LOOKY HERE.

37:47.260 --> 37:50.297
IT'S BUCKO...

37:50.300 --> 37:52.427
AND RUFUS...

37:52.430 --> 37:56.036
AND SHAKES. ..

37:56.040 --> 37:57.462
AND LOLA.

37:57.470 --> 37:59.904
HE'S NOT HERE.

37:59.910 --> 38:03.038
CH ESTER'S NOT HERE.

38:03.040 --> 38:04.576
I'M SORRY.

38:04.580 --> 38:06.138
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

38:06.150 --> 38:08.106
ANYTHING YOU SAY CAN AND WILL
BE USED AGAINST YOU.

38:08.110 --> 38:11.682
YOU CANNOT PROVE THAT
I HAD ANYTHING TO DO WITH THIS!

38:11.690 --> 38:14.409
PLEASE, RESIST ARREST --
PLEASE.

38:14.420 --> 38:15.614
Hans: AAAH!

38:15.620 --> 38:17.087
Mandy: LOOK AT ME!

38:17.090 --> 38:18.421
COME ON.

38:19.690 --> 38:21.499
AAH! AAH!

38:21.500 --> 38:23.149
THAT WAS MY DOG!

38:23.160 --> 38:24.718
YOU KILLED MY DOG!

38:24.730 --> 38:25.924
AAH!

38:25.930 --> 38:27.295
YOU SEE WHAT YOU DID?!

38:27.300 --> 38:28.289
[ GROANS ]

38:28.300 --> 38:29.961
HE WAS MY BEST FRIEND!

38:29.970 --> 38:31.562
AAAAAAH!

38:31.570 --> 38:34.505
HE'S NOT DEAD! I SWEAR!
PLEASE, STOP!

38:34.510 --> 38:35.875
HE'S NOT DEAD?

38:35.880 --> 38:38.747
[ PANTING ]
WE SOLD HIM.

38:38.750 --> 38:42.413
WE SOLD THE DOG
WHEN WE COULDN'T GET A REWARD.

38:53.530 --> 38:55.452
THANK YOU, LEO.

38:55.460 --> 38:56.688
FORGET ABOUT IT.

38:56.700 --> 38:58.622
[ CHUCKLES ] IT WAS FUN.

38:58.630 --> 39:02.691
CAN I ASK YOU
KIND OF A WEIRD QUESTION?

39:02.700 --> 39:05.965
DO YOU ASK
ANY OTHER KIND OF QUESTIONS?

39:05.970 --> 39:09.838
YOU SAID WEEVIL HAD A PEN
ON HIM WHEN HE WAS ARRESTED.

39:09.840 --> 39:12.502
ARE YOU SURE
IT WASN'T A PENCIL?

39:12.510 --> 39:14.444
IT WAS DEFINITELY A PEN.

39:14.450 --> 39:16.475
A PRETTY GIRLY ONE, TOO --

39:16.480 --> 39:19.085
BIG, PINK, PLASTIC.

39:19.090 --> 39:22.958
SO MUCH FOR YOUR BAD BOY.

40:06.430 --> 40:09.797
HONEY, I KNOW YOU DON'T ALWAYS
HAVE A CURFEW THESE DAYS,

40:09.800 --> 40:11.961
BUT YOU'RE STARTING
TO MAKE ME LOOK BAD.

40:11.970 --> 40:14.302
SO YOU KNEW
WEEVIL STALKED LILLY.

40:14.310 --> 40:15.629
YOU QUESTIONED HIM.

40:15.640 --> 40:17.335
WHAT CONVINCED YOU
HE WASN'T THE GUY?

40:17.340 --> 40:20.468
WE SEARCHED HIM, HIS HOME,
DNA -- ALL THAT STUFF.

40:20.480 --> 40:21.947
NOTHING CAME UP.

40:21.950 --> 40:25.545
HE ALSO HAD AN AIRTIGHT ALIBI.
I'LL SHOW YOU.

40:30.320 --> 40:31.719
[ GRUNTS ]

40:31.730 --> 40:33.857
ALL THIS TIME,
YOU'VE HAD LILLY KANE RESEARCH

40:33.860 --> 40:36.727
IN A BOX MARKED "PLAYBOYS"
IN THE CLOSET?

40:36.730 --> 40:39.028
WELL, I FIGURED
IT WOULD BE SAFE THERE.

40:39.030 --> 40:42.864
IT'S THE CLOSED FILES --
JUST THE NONESSENTIAL STUFF.

40:42.870 --> 40:45.600
YOU THINK YOU'RE SLICK,
DON'T YOU?

40:45.610 --> 40:47.498
ONLY 'CAUSE I AM.

40:47.510 --> 40:50.377
OKAY, WEEVIL WAS
ON COMMUNITY SERVICE DETAIL.

40:50.380 --> 40:54.407
A DOZEN PEOPLE SAW HIM
FROM 8:00 AM. TO 2:00 PM.

40:56.080 --> 41:00.039
AND NOW THAT WE KNOW LILLY'S
TIME OF DEATH IS AI-TER 4:00?

41:00.050 --> 41:02.416
THE KANES COVERED UP
LILLY'S MURDER. WE KNOW THAT.

41:02.420 --> 41:06.129
YOU THINK THEY'D GO THROUGH THAT
FOR SOMEONE LIKE WEEVIL?

41:11.600 --> 41:14.125
YOU'VE COME THIS FAR.

41:16.370 --> 41:18.736
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

41:21.580 --> 41:22.729
HI, I'M MANDY.

41:22.740 --> 41:25.379
VERONICA TALKED TO YOU
EARLIER.

41:25.380 --> 41:26.449
[ DOG BARKS ]

41:26.450 --> 41:30.147
CHESTER! OH!

41:30.150 --> 41:31.583
OH!

41:31.590 --> 41:34.115
[ LAUGHS ]

41:38.360 --> 41:39.952
WEEVIL.

41:39.960 --> 41:42.929
THE NIGHT YOU BROKE INTO
THE KANES', I GAVE YOU A PENCIL.

41:42.930 --> 41:44.693
YOU WERE FOUND
WITH A PEN.

41:44.700 --> 41:46.167
THERE WAS NO RING.

41:46.170 --> 41:49.094
YOU FOUND EXACTLY
WHAT YOU WERE LOOKING FOR.

41:49.100 --> 41:51.398
YOU MEAN THIS?

41:51.400 --> 41:53.539
YOU CAN HAVE IT.

41:53.540 --> 41:56.373
ANY MESSAGES INSIDE
WHEN YOU FOUND IT?

41:56.380 --> 41:58.575
MESSAGES FROM YOU, PERHAPS?

41:58.580 --> 42:00.070
NOW, IF I TOLD YOU,

42:00.080 --> 42:04.176
IT WOULDN'T REALLY BE
A SECRET-MESSAGE PEN, WOULD IT?

42:15.060 --> 42:18.518
